{"type":"message","id":"fc93dddc","parentId":"bf424bfc","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:40:09.423Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job context monitor running. Let me read the context monitor script to understand what it's checking and what actions it might take.","thinkingSignature":"2b7ad4f7686e26d94a93a63755448985ee4816a23cad0fc893d5b3e4c5664fc0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q2i97pr7kb6j_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\miliger-context-manager\\scripts\\context-monitor.ps1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":161,"output":78,"cacheRead":37011,"cacheWrite":102,"totalTokens":37352,"cost":{"input":0.00006440000000000001,"output":0.000117,"cacheRead":0.00148044,"cacheWrite":0.0000153,"total":0.00167714}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773920400383}}
{"type":"message","id":"b7be787e","parentId":"fc93dddc","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:40:09.431Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_q2i97pr7kb6j_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Context Monitor for Windows\n# Monitors OpenClaw session context usage and alerts when threshold is reached\n\nparam(\n    [int]$Threshold = 60,\n    [string]$LogDir = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\\logs\",\n    [string]$LogFile = \"$LogDir\\context-monitor.log\"\n)\n\n# Ensure log directory exists\nif (!(Test-Path $LogDir)) {\n    New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $LogDir -Force | Out-Null\n}\n\nfunction Write-Log($Message) {\n    $timestamp = Get-Date -Format \"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\"\n    \"$timestamp - $Message\" | Out-File -Append -FilePath $LogFile\n    Write-Host \"$timestamp - $Message\"\n}\n\n# Get session list to check context usage\ntry {\n    # Use .NET Process to properly separate stdout and stderr\n    $psi = New-Object System.Diagnostics.ProcessStartInfo\n    $psi.FileName = \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\openclaw.cmd\"\n    $psi.Arguments = \"sessions --json\"\n    $psi.RedirectStandardOutput = $true\n    $psi.RedirectStandardError = $true\n    $psi.UseShellExecute = $false\n    $psi.CreateNoWindow = $true\n    \n    $process = New-Object System.Diagnostics.Process\n    $process.StartInfo = $psi\n    $process.Start() | Out-Null\n    \n    $stdout = $process.StandardOutput.ReadToEnd()\n    $stderr = $process.StandardError.ReadToEnd()\n    $process.WaitForExit()\n    \n    if ($stdout) {\n        # Extract JSON from stdout (find content between first { and last })\n        $jsonStart = $stdout.IndexOf('{')\n        $jsonEnd = $stdout.LastIndexOf('}')\n        \n        if ($jsonStart -ge 0 -and $jsonEnd -gt $jsonStart) {\n            $jsonContent = $stdout.Substring($jsonStart, $jsonEnd - $jsonStart + 1)\n            $data = $jsonContent | ConvertFrom-Json -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n            \n            if ($data -and $data.sessions) {\n                # Find main session\n                $mainSession = $data.sessions | Where-Object { $_.key -eq 'agent:main:main' } | Select-Object -First 1\n                \n                if ($mainSession -and $mainSession.totalTokens -and $mainSession.contextTokens) {\n                    $used = $mainSession.totalTokens\n                    $total = $mainSession.contextTokens\n                    $usage = [math]::Round(($used / $total) * 100)\n                    \n                    Write-Log \"Context usage: ${usage}% (${used}/${total} tokens)\"\n                    \n                    if ($usage -ge $Threshold) {\n                        Write-Log \"WARNING: Context usage ${usage}% exceeds threshold ${Threshold}%\"\n                        \n                        # Check memory files\n                        $memoryDir = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\"\n                        $memoryLite = \"$memoryDir\\MEMORY-LITE.md\"\n                        \n                        if (Test-Path $memoryLite) {\n                            $content = Get-Content $memoryLite -Raw -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n                            $wordCount = ($content -split '\\s+').Count\n                            Write-Log \"MEMORY-LITE.md: $wordCount words\"\n                        }\n                        \n                        Write-Log \"ALERT: Consider starting a new session to reset context\"\n                    } else {\n                        Write-Log \"Context usage normal: ${usage}%\"\n                    }\n                } else {\n                    Write-Log \"Main session found but no token info available\"\n                }\n            } else {\n                Write-Log \"No sessions data found in JSON\"\n            }\n        } else {\n            Write-Log \"Could not find JSON content in output\"\n        }\n    } else {\n        Write-Log \"No output from sessions command\"\n    }\n} catch {\n    Write-Log \"Error checking context: $_\"\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773920409429}}
{"type":"message","id":"25d12344","parentId":"b7be787e","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:40:13.952Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a context monitor script that:\n1. Checks the current context/token usage of the main session\n2. Logs the usage percentage\n3. Alerts if it exceeds a threshold (default 60%)\n\nLet me check the log file to see the current context usage and any recent alerts.","thinkingSignature":"913179f13d8e98a9029b3390f5c626e74b4090b5df0d0620206b4b429668259e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ndftlf1o2mn4_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\logs\\context-monitor.log","limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1190,"output":111,"cacheRead":37011,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38312,"cost":{"input":0.000476,"output":0.0001665,"cacheRead":0.00148044,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0021229400000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773920409431}}
{"type":"message","id":"7a5164a3","parentId":"25d12344","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:40:13.957Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ndftlf1o2mn4_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"��2\u00000\u00002\u00006\u0000-\u00000\u00003\u0000-\u00001\u00007\u0000 \u00001\u00006\u0000:\u00002\u00001\u0000:\u00002\u00002\u0000 \u0000-\u0000 \u0000C\u0000o\u0000u\u0000l\u0000d\u0000 \u0000n\u0000o\u0000t\u0000 \u0000p\u0000a\u0000r\u0000s\u0000e\u0000 \u0000c\u0000o\u0000n\u0000t\u0000e\u0000x\u0000t\u0000 \u0000u\u0000s\u0000a\u0000g\u0000e\u0000 \u0000f\u0000r\u0000o\u0000m\u0000 \u0000s\u0000t\u0000a\u0000t\u0000u\u0000s\u0000 \u0000o\u0000u\u0000t\u0000p\u0000u\u0000t\u0000\r\u0000\n\u00002\u00000\u00002\u00006\u0000-\u00000\u00003\u0000-\u00001\u00007\u0000 \u00001\u00006\u0000:\u00002\u00002\u0000:\u00003\u00000\u0000 \u0000-\u0000 \u0000C\u0000o\u0000u\u0000l\u0000d\u0000 \u0000n\u0000o\u0000t\u0000 \u0000f\u0000i\u0000n\u0000d\u0000 \u0000m\u0000a\u0000i\u0000n\u0000 \u0000s\u0000e\u0000s\u0000s\u0000i\u0000o\u0000n\u0000 \u0000c\u0000o\u0000n\u0000t\u0000e\u0000x\u0000t\u0000 \u0000i\u0000n\u0000f\u0000o\u0000\r\u0000\n\u00002\u00000\u00002\u00006\u0000-\u00000\u00003\u0000-\u00001\u00007\u0000 \u00001\u00006\u0000:\u00002\u00003\u0000:\u00004\u00001\u0000 \u0000-\u0000 \u0000E\u0000r\u0000r\u0000o\u0000r\u0000 \u0000c\u0000h\u0000e\u0000c\u0000k\u0000i\u0000n\u0000g\u0000 \u0000c\u0000o\u0000n\u0000t\u0000e\u0000x\u0000t\u0000:\u0000 \u0000�eHe�v \u0000J\u0000S\u0000O\u0000N\u0000 \u0000�WCQ:\u0000 \u0000o\u0000d\u0000e\u0000.\u0000e\u0000x\u0000e\u0000 \u0000:\u0000 \u0000[\u0000p\u0000l\u0000u\u0000g\u0000i\u0000n\u0000s\u0000]\u0000 \u0000p\u0000l\u0000u\u0000g\u0000i\u0000n\u0000s\u0000.\u0000a\u0000l\u0000l\u0000o\u0000w\u0000 \u0000i\u0000s\u0000 \u0000e\u0000m\u0000p\u0000t\u0000y\u0000;\u0000 \u0000d\u0000i\u0000s\u0000c\u0000o\u0000v\u0000e\u0000r\u0000e\u0000d\u0000 \u0000n\u0000o\u0000n\u0000-\u0000b\u0000u\u0000n\u0000d\u0000l\u0000e\u0000d\u0000 \u0000p\u0000l\u0000u\u0000g\u0000i\u0000n\u0000s\u0000 \u0000m\u0000a\u0000y\u0000 \u0000a\u0000u\u0000t\u0000o\u0000-\u0000l\u0000o\u0000a\u0000d\u0000:\u0000 \u0000o\u0000p\u0000e\u0000n\u0000c\u0000l\u0000a\u0000w\u0000-\u0000l\u0000a\u0000r\u0000k\u0000 \u0000(\u0000C\u0000:\u0000\\\u0000U\u0000s\u0000e\u0000r\u0000s\u0000\\\u0000A\u0000d\u0000m\u0000i\u0000\r\u0000\n\u0000n\u0000i\u0000s\u0000t\u0000r\u0000a\u0000t\u0000o\u0000r\u0000\\\u0000.\u0000o\u0000p\u0000e\u0000n\u0000c\u0000l\u0000a\u0000w\u0000\\\u0000e\u0000x\u0000t\u0000e\u0000n\u0000s\u0000i\u0000o\u0000n\u0000s\u0000\\\u0000o\u0000p\u0000e\u0000n\u0000c\u0000l\u0000a\u0000w\u0000-\u0000l\u0000a\u0000r\u0000k\u0000\\\u0000i\u0000n\u0000d\u0000e\u0000x\u0000.\u0000j\u0000s\u0000)\u0000.\u0000 \u0000S\u0000e\u0000t\u0000 \u0000p\u0000l\u0000u\u0000g\u0000i\u0000n\u0000s\u0000.\u0000a\u0000l\u0000l\u0000o\u0000w\u0000 \u0000t\u0000o\u0000 \u0000e\u0000x\u0000p\u0000l\u0000i\u0000c\u0000i\u0000t\u0000 \u0000t\u0000r\u0000u\u0000s\u0000t\u0000e\u0000d\u0000 \u0000i\u0000d\u0000s\u0000.\u0000\r\u0000\n\u0000@b(WMOn \u0000C\u0000:\u0000\\\u0000U\u0000s\u0000e\u0000r\u0000s\u0000\\\u0000A\u0000d\u0000m\u0000i\u0000n\u0000i\u0000s\u0000t\u0000r\u0000a\u0000t\u0000o\u0000r\u0000\\\u0000A\u0000p\u0000p\u0000D\u0000a\u0000t\u0000a\u0000\\\u0000R\u0000o\u0000a\u0000m\u0000i\u0000n\u0000g\u0000\\\u0000n\u0000p\u0000m\u0000\\\u0000o\u0000p\u0000e\u0000n\u0000c\u0000l\u0000a\u0000w\u0000.\u0000p\u0000s\u00001\u0000:\u00002\u00004\u0000 \u0000W[&{:\u0000 \u00005\u0000\r\u0000\n\u0000+\u0000 \u0000 \u0000 \u0000 \u0000 \u0000&\u0000 \u0000\"\u0000n\u0000o\u0000d\u0000e\u0000$\u0000e\u0000x\u0000e\u0000\"\u0000 \u0000 \u0000\"\u0000$\u0000b\u0000a\u0000s\u0000e\u0000d\u0000i\u0000r\u0000/\u0000n\u0000o\u0000d\u0000e\u0000_\u0000m\u0000o\u0000d\u0000u\u0000l\u0000e\u0000s\u0000/\u0000o\u0000p\u0000e\u0000n\u0000c\u0000l\u0000a\u0000w\u0000/\u0000o\u0000p\u0000e\u0000n\u0000c\u0000l\u00